Do NOT move to RAI yet.
Instead, your correct sequence is:
Step 1 (required)
Revise SSS into:
“Perceived Somatic Regulation Self-Efficacy Scale”
Step 2
Standardize item wording (remove physiological control claims)
Step 3
Define factor model (3 correlated subscales, not one engine)
Step 4
Then proceed to RAI
Step 5
Only then design pilot study

Bottom line
Right now your system is at a critical transition point:
